  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators evaluate the changes of echocardiographic and sleep apnea parameters after
      mitral valve surgery. The patients undergo echocardiographic and sleep apnea control before
      surgery. After a period of 3-5 months, they undergo a second echocardiographic and sleep
      apnea control and the results are evaluated.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
